pr_body:
+ All changes unit tested.

<!---
@huboard:{"order":3.375}
-->

Removing the shim config, the library no longer assumes that handlebars is installed. Handlebars is now shipped with the simplelayout library.

Closes https://github.com/4teamwork/ftw.simplelayout/issues/419

@jone could you please test this with ftw.book

Created basic tree tree transformations (rotation, translation) which copy the tree every time they are applied. Rotation and translation are already tested separately. I will have to implement a thorough test for affineTransform when I move it inside neurom.

@lidakanari and everyone please let me know if other functionality is required as well.

@juanchopanza I am unsure where these functions should be moved. I would say morphtree but morphtree is in analysis and this is a little bit more invasive than analysis.

In example part,   
vapid_claims={
                "sub": "YourNameHere@example.org",
            }
It will lead to an error which lacks "mailto" fields.
